<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-412] About Max OSTs Size. 256TB vs 256TiB</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-412</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello~ Recently, I have question about the MAX osts size..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;According to lustre manual.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Page 4, Max OSTs Size 256TB (zfs) ==&amp;gt; 232.831TiB&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Page 32 , Max OSTs Size 256TiB (zfs) ==&amp;gt; 281.475TB&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would you please guide which is correct? Can I use 256TiB? or use 256TB?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks..&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
